name: Space Survival (itch) (preetish)
description:
Griffin is one of the animals which is extinct now. Luckily, we found one in space. But an evil hunter wants to kill him. 

"Guys go and save our hero"

This is a survival game with 7 levels.  A player has to complete all 7 levels to win this game.

But its near to impossible to everyone to win this game. If you likes challenge, go and try to win it.

 "Best of Luck"
